e kei te tika te mahi a tō tūhononga ipurangi. </li>
    <li> Whakapā atu ki te kaipupuri o te paetukutuku. </li>
    </ol>Kimi āwhina mō te karere tauwhāiti hapaKāore tō tūhononga i te tūmataiti, tērā rānei "<span class="error-code">NET::ERR_CERT_AUTHORITY_INVALID</span>" tērā rānei "<span class="error-code">ERR_CERT_COMMON_NAME_INVALID</span>" tērā rānei "<span class="error-code">NET::ERR_CERT_WEAK_SIGNATURE_ALGORITHM</span>" tērā rānei "<span class="error-code">ERR_CERT_SYMANTEC_LEGACY</span>" tērā rānei "Hapa tiwhikete SSL"Kei te tōmuri tō karaka, "Kei te tōmua tō karaka" rānei, tērā rānei "<span class="error-code">NET::ERR_CERT_DATE_INVALID</span>"<h4>Hipanga 1: Takiuru ki te tomokanga</h4>
    <p> E hiahia ana ngā whatunga Wi-fi i ngā wāhi pēnei i te wharekai, ngā taunga waka rererang kia takiuru koe. Hei kite i te whārangi takiuru, haere ki tētahi whārangi e whakamahi ana i <code>http://</code>.</p>
    <ol>
    <li> Haere ki tētahi paetukutuku ka tīmata ki te <code>http://</code> pēnei i <a href="http://example.com" target="_blank">http://example.com</a>.</li>
    <li>Kei te whārangi takiuru e huaki nei, takiuru ki te whakamahi i te ipurangi. </li>
    </ol>
    <h4> Hipanga 2: Whakatuwheratia te whārangi i te aratau InPrivate (rorohiko anake) </h4>
    <p> Mēnā ka whakatuwherahe whārangi, kāore e tika ana te mahi a tētahi toronga. Hei whakatika i te hapa, me whakaweto te toronga.</p>
    <h4>Hipanga 3: Whakahōutia tō pūnaha whakahaere </h4>
    <p>Whakarite kei te hōu tonu tō pūrere.</p>
    <h4>Hipanga 4: Whakaweto rangitahitia tō pareketo </h4>
    <p> Ka kite koe i tēnei hapa mēnā kei a koe he papatonopareketo ka whakarato i te "parenga HTTPS", te "karapa HTTPS" rānei. Kei te ārai te pareketo i tā Microsoft Edge whakarato i te haumaru.</p>
    <p> Hei whakatika i te raru, whakawetohia i tō pūmanawa pareketo. Mēnā e pai ana te whārangi i muri i te whakaweto i te pūmanawa, whakawetotia taua pūmanawa ina whakamahi koe i ngā pae haumaru.</p>
    <p> Maumahara ki te whakakā anō i tō papatono pareketo ina oti koe.</p>
    <h4>Hipanga 5: Tiki āwhina anō </h4>
    <p> Mēnā ka kite tonu koe i te hapa, whakapā atu ki te kaipupuri o te paetukutuku.</p><p>Ka kite koe i tēnei hapa mēnā ka whakamahi koe i tētahi tomokanga Wi-Fi me takiuru koe i mua i te haere tuihono.</p>
    <p>Hei whakatika i te hapa, pāwhiri Tūhono <strong></strong> i te whārangi e ngana ana ai ki te haere.</p><p>Ka kite koe i tēnei hapa mēnā kei te hē te rā me te wā i runga i tō rorohiko, tō pūrere pūkoro rānei. </p>
 <p> Hei whakatika i te hapa, whakatuwheratia tō karaka pūrere. Me mātua whakarite kei te tika te wā me te rā.</p>Kei te ārai he pūmanawa i tō rorohiko i te tūhono haumaru a Microsoft Edge ki te tukutuku (i ngā rorohiko Windows anake)<p>Ka kite koe i tēnei hapa mēnā kei a koe ngā pūmanawa Superfish i tō rorohiko Windows.</p>
      <p>Whāia ēnei hipanga kia whakaweto rangitahitia te pūmanawa kia taea ai te tukutuku. Me whai whakaaetanga kaiwhakahaere.</p>
